### "The Operator Playbook" para Newsletters B2B
* **Señal Técnica:** Framework operativo impulsado por IA para transformar grabaciones de llamadas en activos de retención en 30 minutos.
* **Contenido Crudo:**
> Most b2b newsletters aren't newsletters. They're 3 blogs in a trench coat. That's a marketing email. Once your audience sees that, they stop opening it.
> 
> Here's how to start creating newsletters that actually get read:
> 1. Record your calls during the week.
> 2. Pipe all of the recordings into Claude.
> 3. Ask it to pull frameworks and templates you referenced.
> 4. Upload your voiceprint.
> 5. Draft a bad first draft and punch it up for 30min.
> 
> Newsletters are meant to be a relationship loop that makes you the default choice when your audience is in a buying motion.

